features: √ONE BUTTON SEARCHING: Operate the tracker with your cell phone and it will make a sound so you can quickly find what you can't find. Press the button on the tracker and your cell phone will beep to help you find it quickly.

√FIND LOST THINGS FAST: This smart GPS tracker and Bluetooth loss prevention device will alert you when you're about to forget your belongings. Connect it to your cell phone and key locator and both will ring to alert you once you disconnect. Ideal for traveling to avoid loss.

√COMPATIBLE WITH YOUR DEVICE: Our ultra-lightweight, no-frills tracker supports iOS and Android 4.3 or later (Bluetooth 4.0 required). Download the "iSearching" app from the App Store or scan the QR code included in the manual to download the software.

√REMOTE CAMERA FUNCTION: This key finder wireless smart tracker can be used as a remote shutter to make selfies more convenient and capture some happy moments easily. It can also help you take wide-angle beautiful photos through the front or rear camera.
√SERVICE AFTER SALE: If there is any problem, please feel free to contact us, we will do our best to solve the problem for you
body.description: Do you have the same problem?Where's my pet?Where's my phone?Where are my keys?Where's the TV remote?Where did I put my camera?Where's my wallet?……This tracker of ours can easily solve your problem!You can hang it where you can, or attach it with double-sided tape to something you want to track, and use your phone to locate it both ways!Makes finding things quick and easy
